extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div
      h1 Hey, Prospective Employer!
      p.lead.text-light
        | This portfolio is a marketing document meant to demonstrate my myriad skills, including, but not limited to: web development, soft skills, lifelong learning, technical prowess, and the ability to use the word "myriad" correctly in a sentence. Am I hired? 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3
      each project in projects
        .cell
          a(href='/projects/' + project.id)
            img.thumbnail(src='https://placehold.it/550x550')
            h5 #{project.project_name}
